# Ambient Music Directory

This directory contains ambient background music files for the D&D Campaign Manager.

## Required Ambient Track Files

Place the following MP3 files in this directory:

- tavern.mp3 - Tavern/inn atmosphere
- town.mp3 - Town/city atmosphere
- peaceful.mp3 - Peaceful/calm atmosphere
- forest.mp3 - Forest/wilderness atmosphere
- dungeon.mp3 - Dungeon/underground atmosphere
- cave.mp3 - Cave atmosphere
- mystical.mp3 - Mystical/magical atmosphere
- combat.mp3 - Combat music (general)
- boss-battle.mp3 - Epic boss battle music

## Recommendations

- Use loopable tracks (seamless loops)
- Keep file sizes reasonable (consider compressed MP3 format)
- Typical length: 2-5 minutes per track
- Volume: Normalize to consistent levels

